Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃命似的離家出走 再被Veda選上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有就不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那理坦德呢
