Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為有保密義務嘛 不過今非昔比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh的整備呢
