Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給洛克昂的信寫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.54,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂收
